data.description: Seller has relocated and is ready to receive your offers. Small town living and a spacious, updated home await you. Add this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home to your must see list! As you walk through you'll find updated flooring, fresh paint and a fully refreshed kitchen (paint, counters, backsplash). The home has been updated throughout so you can move right in and make it your own. 2 living spaces, formal dining, kitchen w/breakfast nook & a split bedroom plan give you the space you desire. The attached 2 car garage includes 2 rooms that could be used for craft or hobby areas. Property includes a large pole barn w/electric service for boat or RV parking. Pole barn includes a 2nd floor storage space and could be finished inside to host a home gym, hobby area and more. 4 total parcels w/a fenced area.
